long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
LuxNet is a private web network of hundreds of websites.
LuxNet is a community managed and created network that
is not affiliated with any of the companies outside it.
We ensure that none of your information and data won't be sold
There are no rules in LuxNet, your website will be private for LuxNet users
and it won't be closed or cancelled.
